        <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
        <h2>Rooted in Fayetteville. Grown with its families.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Azalea Estates has been the preferred blended community for independent and assisted living residents in Fayette County for over 30 years. We&rsquo;re proud to have grown alongside the people we serve.</p>
        <p>Our one-story campus was designed with seniors in mind &mdash; no elevators, no stairs, and every shared space just a short walk away. The result is a community that feels unmistakably like a neighborhood: easy, familiar, connected.</p>
        <p>We believe that aging well is a team effort. That&rsquo;s why we partner with families, physicians, local churches, schools, civic organizations, and the greater Atlanta community to fill each day with meaning. Whether you&rsquo;re exploring <a href="/living-options/">our living options</a> or curious about the <a href="/amenities/">services and amenities we provide</a>, we&rsquo;re happy to walk you through it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
