<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="prose reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Licensed &amp; Trusted</span>
      <h2>One of only two licensed assisted living providers in Fayette County.</h2>
      <p>Azalea Estates holds an Assisted Living License from the State of Georgia &mdash; not a Personal Care Home designation. Our licensed registered nurse and LPN staff provide up to 16 hours of nursing care daily, and our 24-hour on-site staffing means medical support is always within reach. Learn more about <a href="/living-options/assisted-living/">our licensed assisted living program</a>.</p>
      <p>Our approach blends homelike comfort with clinical competence: individualized care plans, medication management in partnership with third-party providers, wireless call pendants, and bathroom pull-cord response systems.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

