      <h2>Serving Fayette County and the Southern Crescent region.</h2>
      <p>Azalea Estates of Fayetteville is located at 105 Autumn Glen Circle, just off Highway 54 in Fayetteville, Georgia &mdash; the heart of Fayette County. We are approximately 13 miles from Peachtree City, 30 miles south of Atlanta, and conveniently accessible from throughout the Southern Crescent.</p>
      <p>Families from Peachtree City, Tyrone, Brooks, Woolsey, Senoia, Newnan, and greater Atlanta have trusted us with their loved ones for more than three decades. If you&rsquo;re searching for senior living in Fayette County or the surrounding area, we would be honored to meet you.</p>
      <p>Our address: <strong>105 Autumn Glen Circle, Fayetteville, GA 30215</strong> &middot; <a href="tel:{{ site.contact.phoneRaw }}">{{ site.contact.phone }}</a></p>
